name: Into The Deep (Mataiaz)
description:
You like fish?

This game was intended for the ScoreSpace game jam#23 in 2022.

All assets where self made except the noise the fish make.

The game did not get released in time because I failed to realise that the game has to be played in the browser.  Right before the game jam ended I was stuck watching a loading bar for converting my game into a browser game..
